        <abstract>
            <p>Has no letters or papers [of Erasmus Darwin].</p> 
<p>Suggests CD cite some of Erasmus Darwin’s poems to answer the charge of atheism [see <hi rend="italic">Erasmus Darwin</hi>, p. 44].</p> 
            <p>Recounts a story of a remarkable cure by Dr Darwin, showing his sagacity and daring.</p>
        </abstract>
